<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Neon Grid Runner - Hacker Protocol</title>
    <!-- Supabase JS Client CDN -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@supabase/supabase-js@2"></script>
    <!-- Google Fonts for Retro Arcade Style -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron:wght@400;700;900&family=Press+Start+2P&family=Share+Tech+Mono&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="arcade-wrapper">
        <!-- LEFT: About Retro / Developer Profile Panel -->
        <div class="profile-panel side-panel">
            <div class="dashboard-card" style="padding: 20px;">
                <div class="profile-avatar-card">
                    <div class="avatar-frame" style="border-color: var(--neon-blue); box-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--neon-blue);">
                        <!-- Retro Gamepad Icon -->
                        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path fill="currentColor" d="M21,6H3A2,2 0 0,0 1,8V16A2,2 0 0,0 3,18H21A2,2 0 0,0 23,16V8A2,2 0 0,0 21,6M6,15A3,3 0 1,1 9,12A3,3 0 0,1 6,15M18,11A1,1 0 1,1 17,12A1,1 0 0,1 18,11M20,13A1,1 0 1,1 19,14A1,1 0 0,1 20,13Z" />
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h2 class="profile-title">NEON RETRO</h2>
                    <span class="profile-subtitle" style="color: var(--neon-blue);">80S REGENERATION</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="bio-text" style="margin-top: 14px; text-align: left; font-size: 0.72rem; line-height: 1.4;">
                    <p style="margin-bottom: 10px; color: #fff;"><strong>Grid Runner</strong> is a modern cybernetic reconstruction of the legendary 80s arcade maze-chase genre.</p>
                    <p style="color: #a8a8cf;">Our mission under the <strong>Old Men Coding</strong> banner is to regenerate the greatest gameplay formulas of the 1980s—reimagining them with vibrant neon aesthetics, synthwave audio, and custom tactical twists to offer a fresh challenge.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Coming Soon Card -->
            <div class="dashboard-card" style="padding: 16px;">
                <div class="card-header" style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 8px;">
                    <h3 class="neon-pink" style="font-family: var(--font-title); font-size: 0.58rem; letter-spacing: 0.5px;">COMING SOON</h3>
                </div>
                <p style="font-size: 0.7rem; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 4px; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;">🕹️ Kong Climb</p>
                <p style="font-size: 0.68rem; color: #8080a0; text-align: center; line-height: 1.35;">A hybrid vertical platforms-climber fused with space shooter defense systems and hover highways.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Support Card -->
            <div class="dashboard-card" style="padding: 16px; text-align: center;">
                <div class="card-header" style="margin-bottom: 8px;">
                    <h3 class="neon-yellow-text" style="font-family: var(--font-title); font-size: 0.58rem; letter-spacing: 0.5px;">⚡ SUPPORT THE PORTAL</h3>
                </div>
                <p style="font-size: 0.68rem; color: #a8a8cf; line-height: 1.35; margin-bottom: 12px;">Support the development of new retro game cabinets by buying the developer a coffee.</p>
                <a href="https://ko-fi.com/oldmencoding" target="_blank" class="arcade-btn" style="text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; font-size: 0.58rem; padding: 10px 0; width: 100%; box-shadow: 0 4px 0 #6d0034;">☕ Buy Mike a Coffee</a>
            </div>

            <!-- Disclaimer footer -->
            <div style="font-size: 0.62rem; color: #505075; line-height: 1.35; text-align: center; padding: 8px 6px; border-top: 1px solid #1a1a3a;">
                <strong style="color: #6a6a9f; display: block; margin-bottom: 4px; font-family: var(--font-hud); font-size: 0.5rem; letter-spacing: 0.5px;">OLD MEN CODING</strong>
                Handcrafting and evolving classic retro gaming formulas with neon visual overhauls.
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Main Cabinet Container -->
        <div class="arcade-container">
            <!-- Arcade Cabinet Header / Neon Sign -->
            <header class="arcade-header">
                <h1 class="neon-text" data-text="NEON ARCADE">NEON ARCADE</h1>
                <p class="neon-subtitle">RETRO CHIP EDITION</p>
                <div style="margin-top: 8px;">
                    <a href="index.html" class="footer-link" style="text-decoration: none; padding: 4px 10px; background: rgba(0, 243, 255, 0.1); border: 1px solid var(--neon-blue); border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.7rem; font-family: var(--font-hud); letter-spacing: 0.5px; color: var(--neon-blue); display: inline-block;">🕹️ BACK TO LOBBY</a>
                </div>
            </header>

            <!-- Main Cabinet Body -->
            <div class="cabinet-body">
                <!-- Glass Screen Bezel -->
                <div class="screen-bezel">
                    <!-- Retro CRT Scanline Overlay -->
                    <div class="crt-overlay"></div>
                    
                    <!-- Game Header HUD -->
                    <div class="hud-container">
                        <div class="hud-item score-board">
                            <span class="hud-label">SCORE</span>
                            <span id="score" class="hud-value neon-green">000000</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="hud-item high-score-board">
                            <span class="hud-label">HIGH SCORE</span>
                            <span id="high-score" class="hud-value neon-pink">000000</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="hud-item lives-board">
                            <span class="hud-label">INTEGRITY</span>
                            <div id="lives-container" class="lives-icons">
                                <!-- JS will inject system core icons here -->
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Screen Screen Content (Canvas & Overlays) -->
                    <div class="screen-content">
                        <canvas id="gameCanvas" width="512" height="544"></canvas>

                        <!-- Game Screen Overlay (Start/Pause/GameOver) -->
                        <div id="overlay" class="game-overlay active">
                            <div class="overlay-card">
                                <h2 id="overlay-title" class="neon-yellow">INITIALIZE GRID RUN</h2>
                                <div class="difficulty-container">
                                    <span class="diff-label">DIFFICULTY:</span>
                                    <div class="diff-options">
                                        <button id="diff-easy" class="diff-btn">EASY</button>
                                        <button id="diff-normal" class="diff-btn active">NORMAL</button>
                                        <button id="diff-hard" class="diff-btn">HARD</button>
                                        <button id="diff-insane" class="diff-btn">INSANE</button>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <p id="overlay-message">USE ARROWS OR WASD TO RUN PROTOCOL</p>
                                <button id="start-btn" class="arcade-btn">INITIALIZE RUN</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Game Footer HUD -->
                    <div class="hud-footer">
                        <div class="hud-item">
                            <span class="hud-label">LEVEL</span>
                            <span id="level" class="hud-value neon-blue">1</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="hud-item">
                            <span class="hud-label">DIFFICULTY</span>
                            <span id="hud-difficulty" class="hud-value neon-green">NORMAL</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="hud-item">
                            <span class="hud-label">STATUS</span>
                            <span id="status-text" class="hud-value neon-yellow">INSERT COIN</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Controls/Instruction Bezel -->
            <div class="cabinet-lower-panel">
                <div class="joystick-graphics">
                    <div class="joystick-base">
                        <div class="joystick-ball"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="action-buttons">
                        <div class="action-btn-red"></div>
                        <div class="action-btn-blue"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="cabinet-instructions">
                    <h3>HOW TO PLAY</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Use <span class="key-cap">▲</span> <span class="key-cap">▼</span> <span class="key-cap">◀</span> <span class="key-cap">▶</span> or <span class="key-cap">W</span> <span class="key-cap">A</span> <span class="key-cap">S</span> <span class="key-cap">D</span> to steer core.</li>
                        <li>Download all <span class="pellet-highlight">Byte Packets</span> to clear the node grid.</li>
                        <li>Decrypt <span class="pellet-highlight">Overclock Modules</span> to overload sentinel firewalls.</li>
                        <li>Avoid sentinels or suffer core integrity collapse!</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Audio and Action Buttons -->
            <div class="system-controls">
                <button id="mute-btn" class="system-btn">🔊 Mute</button>
                <button id="pause-btn" class="system-btn" disabled>⏸ Pause</button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Side Panel for Global Leaderboard & Authentication -->
        <div class="side-panel">
            <!-- Connection Status Indicator -->
            <div class="panel-header">
                <span class="status-indicator-label">SUPABASE DATABASE:</span>
                <span id="db-status" class="status-indicator offline">OFFLINE</span>
            </div>

            <!-- Auth Section -->
            <div class="auth-section card">
                <div id="auth-logged-out">
                    <h3 class="panel-title neon-pink-text">PLAYER AUTH</h3>
                    
                    <div class="auth-toggle">
                        <button id="toggle-login-btn" class="toggle-btn active">LOGIN</button>
                        <button id="toggle-register-btn" class="toggle-btn">REGISTER</button>
                    </div>

                    <form id="auth-form" class="auth-form">
                        <div class="input-group" id="username-group" style="display: none;">
                            <label for="auth-username">USERNAME</label>
                            <input type="text" id="auth-username" autocomplete="off" placeholder="GRID_RUNNER_99">
                        </div>
                        <div class="input-group">
                            <label for="auth-email">EMAIL</label>
                            <input type="email" id="auth-email" required placeholder="player@email.com">
                        </div>
                        <div class="input-group">
                            <label for="auth-password">PASSWORD</label>
                            <input type="password" id="auth-password" required placeholder="******">
                        </div>
                        <button type="submit" id="auth-submit-btn" class="arcade-btn-mini">SUBMIT</button>
                    </form>
                    <div id="auth-error-msg" class="auth-error"></div>
                </div>

                <div id="auth-logged-in" style="display: none;">
                    <h3 class="panel-title neon-green-text">PLAYER PROFILE</h3>
                    <div class="profile-info">
                        <span class="profile-label">PLAYER:</span>
                        <span id="player-username" class="profile-value neon-yellow-text">-</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="profile-info">
                        <span class="profile-label">PERSONAL BEST:</span>
                        <span id="player-pb" class="profile-value neon-blue-text">000000</span>
                    </div>
                    <button id="logout-btn" class="arcade-btn-mini reset-btn">LOG OUT</button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Leaderboard Section -->
            <div class="leaderboard-section card">
                <h3 class="panel-title neon-cyan-text">GLOBAL TOP 10</h3>
                <div class="leaderboard-table-container">
                    <table class="leaderboard-table">
                        <thead>
                            <tr>
                                <th>RK</th>
                                <th>PLAYER</th>
                                <th>SCORE</th>
                            </tr>
                        </thead>
                        <tbody id="leaderboard-body">
                            <tr><td colspan="3" class="loading-text">LOADING SCORES...</td></tr>
                        </tbody>
                    </table>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Panel Footer -->
            <div class="panel-footer">
                <button id="reset-config-btn" class="footer-link">🔧 Configure Custom Database</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Supabase Setup Configuration Modal -->
    <div id="setup-modal" class="setup-overlay">
        <div class="setup-card">
            <h2 class="neon-yellow-text">CONNECT TO SUPABASE</h2>
            <p>Connect your own Supabase instance to store global high scores and enable account registration.</p>
            
            <form id="setup-form" class="setup-form">
                <div class="input-group">
                    <label for="setup-url">SUPABASE URL</label>
                    <input type="url" id="setup-url" required placeholder="https://your-project-id.supabase.co" autocomplete="off">
                </div>
                <div class="input-group">
                    <label for="setup-key">SUPABASE ANON KEY</label>
                    <input type="text" id="setup-key" required placeholder="eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..." autocomplete="off">
                </div>
                
                <div class="setup-instructions">
                    <h4>How to get keys:</h4>
                    <ol>
                        <li>Log in to your <strong>Supabase Dashboard</strong>.</li>
                        <li>Select your project, go to <strong>Project Settings</strong> &gt; <strong>API</strong>.</li>
                        <li>Copy the <strong>Project URL</strong> and the <strong>anon public API key</strong>.</li>
                    </ol>
                </div>
                
                <button type="submit" class="arcade-btn">SAVE & CONNECT</button>
                
                <div style="display: flex; gap: 10px; width: 100%; justify-content: center; margin-top: 6px;">
                    <button type="button" id="use-default-btn" class="arcade-btn" style="flex: 1; background: rgba(0, 243, 255, 0.15); border-color: var(--neon-blue); color: #fff; font-size: 0.7rem; padding: 10px 0;">RESET TO DEFAULT</button>
                    <button type="button" id="close-setup-btn" class="arcade-btn" style="flex: 1; background: rgba(255, 0, 127, 0.15); border-color: var(--neon-pink); color: #fff; font-size: 0.7rem; padding: 10px 0;">CANCEL</button>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Web Application Logic -->
    <script src="game.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
